{"schemaVersion":1,"source":"docfx-mref-page","file":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.yml","symbols":[{"uid":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions","name":"CorsPolicyOptions","fullName":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions","kind":"Class","namespace":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web","assembly":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web","summary":"Options for configuring a CORS policy.","remarks":"Defines what origins, methods, headers, and credentials are allowed for cross-origin requests. Null values for boolean properties are treated as false (feature not enabled). Configure policies based on your security requirements: - Production: Use specific BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowedOrigins with BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowCredentials = true - Development: Use BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowAnyOrigin = true (without credentials) or specific localhost origins - Public APIs: Use BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowAnyOrigin = true (without credentials)","syntax":{"content":"public class CorsPolicyOptions","parameters":[],"returns":null},"parameters":[],"returns":null,"parent":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web","children":["BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.#ctor","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowAnyHeader","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowAnyMethod","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowAnyOrigin","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowCredentials","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowWildcardSubdomains","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowedHeaders","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowedMethods","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.AllowedOrigins","BridgingIT.DevKit.Presentation.Web.CorsPolicyOptions.ExposeHeaders","Br